{"title":"首都人人唱炼钢","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":12,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"首都人人唱炼钢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人面钢花相映红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲天烈火照星空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疑是东方旭日升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熊熊炉火放异彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人面钢花相映红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京汽车制造厂工人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于世河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深夜红光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日落西山夜幕临，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜来西边出彩云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为何太阳从西起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来是钢水照天明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京汽车制造厂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吕宝珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高炉当绣房"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘日夜忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高炉当绣房。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丢掉绣花针，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿起铁棍棒；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问她巧手绣什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她说绣的钢花闪金"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京宣武钢厂电工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘树珍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是太阳出来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么照得屋里亮？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小明惊醒跳下床，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拍着妈妈大声喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“东方太阳出来了。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×  ×  ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈一看微微笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“宝宝快快来睡觉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是太阳出来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是爸爸在炼钢。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京印刷一厂排字工人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小  兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜  战"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上星斗齐吵嚷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为何大地冒金光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽听夜游神来报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三厂英雄在炼钢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京皮毛三厂机缝工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郑金荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈炼钢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈放下孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子睡得很香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“睡吧小宝贝儿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈去炼钢。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×  ×  ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈回来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子含着乳头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又进入了梦乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈喝了口水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又急忙跑回钢炉旁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×  ×  ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等你炼钢时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐在远距离的操纵室"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不要忘记呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把妈妈和全民炼钢的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故事讲一讲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京工人技术学校"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周夫路终身愿把矿山伴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风镐凿开千座山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见矿石心不甘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高楼大厦我不恋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终身愿把矿山伴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁学院学生"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}